# The [[grass]] ''[[Chrysopogon zizanioides]]'' ( <= {{taxlink|Vetiveria zizanioides|species|noshow=1}}), which is native to [[India]], but planted throughout the tropics for its fragrant roots and for erosion control.
#* '''2003''', Anand Akhila, Mumkum Rani, ''4: Chemical Conatituents and Essential Oil Biogenisis in Vetiveria zizanioides'', Massimo Maffei (editor), ''Vetiveria: The Genus Vetiveria'', [http://books.google.com.au/books?id=SMXV-FFQlpcC&pg=PA73&dq=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jZ-FU6z9KcvNlAWxoID4Bg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&f=false page 73],
