#* '''2007''', R. Sinha, ''et al.'', ''Phytoremediation: Role of Plants in Site Management'', S.N. Singh, R. D. Tripathi, ''Environmental Bioremediation Technologies'', [http://books.google.com.au/books?id=DY66MkyLriEC&pg=PA328&dq=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jZ-FU6z9KcvNlAWxoID4Bg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&f=false page 328],
