#* '''2008''', Humberto Blanco-Canqui, ''Principles of Soil Conservation and Management'', [http://books.google.com.au/books?id=Wj3690PbDY0C&pg=PA237&dq=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jZ-FU6z9KcvNlAWxoID4Bg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22vetiver%22%7C%22vetivers%22&f=false page 237],
